name: MojoMojo Overdrive
details:
Overdrive Pedal with Extra HeadroomA pedal that sounds like an amp, with a very open character and little compression allowing even the most subtle of your playing to shine through. We basically set out to capture lightning in a bottle with a clarity that even allowed for complex chords to stand out – did we succeed? Well, plug it in, play one lick, look us in the eye and try to tell us we didn’t!
•    Increased circuit board voltage for extra headroom
    •    Precise tone controls
    •    Voicing switch
